@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rsvzpc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (v0 * ((v0 + 0.96 / tmp + 0.18) - tmp))
    v1 = (wp.sin(v0) - wp.cos((v2 + 0.45 + v0 + 0.53)))
    v2 = wp.exp(v0)
    v0 = (v1 + (wp.exp(v1 + 0.27) * (tmp + 0.04 + tmp + 0.54)))
    v1 = (v2 / tmp)
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.abs(v2 + 0.41) - v1))
    v2 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.58 / v0 + 0.26)) * ((tmp + 0.02 / v1 + 0.39) * 0.28))
    v0 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
